[{"Id": 1013733, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Sadiq (a) says, when you intended to go for Ziyarat of Imam Husain (a), perform Ghusl (spiritual bath) in Furaat (the Messenger of Allah (s) said, He who washes himself in Furaat (intending to visit the tomb of Husain) will have all of his sins eradicated as if he has just been born if possible or at your stay in karbala. As you wash yourself recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Sadiq (a) farmate hai, jab tum Imam Husain (a) ki ziyarat ka iraada karo to Furaat par ghusl anjaam do. Rasool-e-Khuda (s) farmaate hai keh, jo shakhs ziyarat Imam Husain (a) ko jaaye aur furaat mein ghusl kare, to uske gunah is tarah dhul jaayenge jaisa keh woh paiydaaish ke waqt paak tha. Agar Furaat par ghusl mumkeen na ho to Karbala mein apne thairne ke maqaam par ghusl kare to us dauraan yeh dua padhe…", "UrduDescription": "امام جعفر صادق ؑنے فرمایا : جب امام حسینؑ کے حرم میں جانے کا ارادا کرو تو فرات کے کنارے پہنچو تو وہاں غسل کرو،کیوں کہ میرے پدر گرامی نے اپنے والد ماجد سے اور انہوں نے حضرت رسول ؐسے خبر دی ہے کہ آنحضرتؐ نے فرمایا: میرا بیٹا حسینؑ میرے بعد فرات کے کنارے شہید کیا جائے گا۔ لہٰذا جو شخص ان کی زیارت کو جائے اور فرات میں غسل کرے تو اس کے گناہ اس طرح دھل جائیں گے جیسے وہ اپنی ماں کے پیٹ سے پیدا ہوا تھا۔ جب وہ دریائے فرات پر غسل کرے تواس دوران یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013734, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khuda ke naam aur Khuda ki zaat se, ay Ma’bood! Qaraar de is ghusl ko roshan, paakeeza aur shafa dene waala har maraz, har bimaari, har aafat aur har buraayi se bacha ne waala. Ay Ma’bood! Paak kar de is se mere dil ko, khol de is se mere seene ko aur aasaan kar de uske zariye mera kaam.", "Urdu": "خدا کے نام اور خدا کی ذات سے اے معبود! قرار دے اس غسل کو روشن پاکیزہ اور شفا دینے والا ہر مرض ہر بیماری ہر آفت اور ہربرائی سے بچانے والا اے معبود! پاک کر دے اس سے میرے دل کو کھول دے اس سے میرے سینے کو اور اس کے ذریعے میرا کام آسان کردے۔", "RArabic": "BIMSIL LAAHE WA BILLAAHE ALLAAHUMMAJ A’LHO NOORAWN WA TAHOORAWN WA HIRZAWN WA SHEFAA-AM MIN KULLE DAAA-IN WA SUQMIN WA AAFATIN WA A’AHATIN ALLAAHUMMA TAHHIR BEHI QALBEE WASH-RAH BEHI SADREE WA SAHHIL LEE BEHI AMREE.", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللهِ وَبِاللهِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اجْعَلْهُ نُوْرًا وَطَهُوْرًا وَحِرْزًا وَشِفَاءً مِنْ كُلِّ دَاءٍ وَسُقْمٍ وَآفَةٍ وَعَاهَةٍ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ طَهِّرْ بِهٖ قَلْبِيْ وَاشْرَحْ بِهٖ صَدْرِيْ وَسَهِّلْ لِيْ بِهٖ اَمْرِيْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018144, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "Wear pure clothes, but do not apply perfume and offer 2 rakat namaz. Now move towards the shrine with tranquility and solemnity. As you walk, try to make short steps, for Allah (s.w.t) shall record for you the reward of going on Hajj and Umrah. Try to be pious hearted with tearful eyes and while walking recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Paak o saaf libaas pehne, magar khushboo na lagaaye aur 2 rakat namaz adaa kare. Ab Haram mubarak ki taraf aahista aahista qadam badaaye kyu’n keh Khuda taala ek ek qadam ke badle mein Hajj o Umrah ka sawaab ataa karega. Chalte huwe nehaayat aajezi o inkesaari ke saath padhe…", "UrduDescription": "جب غسل کر چکے تو پاکیزہ لباس پہنے اور اس دریا کے کنارے دو رکعت نماز بجا لائے کہ یہ وہی زمین ہے جس کی شان خدا نے بیان کی ہے اورزمین کے کئی حصے آپس میں ملے ہوئے ہوتے ہیں، انگور کے باغ کھیتی اور کھجور کے درخت کہ بعض کی ایک جڑ دو شاخیں اور بعض کی ایک شاخ جب کہ وہ سب ایک ہی پانی سے سیراب کیے جاتے ہیں اور میووں میں سے بعض کو بعض پر ہم فوقیت وبرتری دیتے ہیں، جب نماز پڑھ لے تو امام حسینؑ کے حرم مبارک کی طرف آہستہ آہستہ چل کر جائے، کیوں کہ خدا تعالیٰ ایک ایک قدم کے بدلے میں حج و عمرہ کا ثواب عطا کرے گا چلتے ہوئے نہایت عاجز ی و انکساری کے ساتھ ذکرِ خدا اور گریہ و زاری کرتا جائے  اور کہے ۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018145, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the name of Allah, and all praise is for Allah, and there is no god but Allah, and Allah is greatest. O Allah send blessings upon Muhammad (s.a.w.a) and upon the progeny of Muhammad (a.s). Allah’s salutation on Husain (a.s) and on the children of Husain (a.s) and on the companions of Husain (a.s). And cursed of Allah be upon his enemies and upon his killers.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Allah ke naam se aur hamd Allah hi ke liye, aur nahin koi ma’bood siwaaye Allah ke, aur Allah buzurg-tar hai. Ay Allah rehmat naazil farma Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) par. Allah ka salaam ho Husain (a.s) par aur Husain (a.s) ki aulaado’n par aur Husain (a.s) ke saathiyo’n par. Aur Allah ki laanat ho unke tamaam dushmano aur qaatilo’n par.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے اور حمد اللہ ہی کے لئے اور نہیں کوئی معبود سوائے اللہ کے، اور اللہ بزرگتر ہے۔ اے اللہ رحمت نازل فرما حضرت محمدؐ اور آلِ محمدؑ پر۔ اللہ کا سلام ہو حسینؑ پر اور حسینؑ کی اولادوں پر اور  حسینؑ کےساتھیوں پر۔ اور اللہ کی لعنت ہو ان کے تمام دشمنوں اور قاتلوں پر۔", "RArabic": "BISMIL-LAAHE WAL-HAMDO LILLAAHE WALAA ILAAHA ILLAL-LAAHO WAL-LAAHO AKBARO, ALLAAHUMMA SALLE ALAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMDIN, SALAA-MUL LAAHE A’LAL HUSAINE WA A’LAA AWLAA-DIL HUSAINE WA A’LAA AS-HAA-BIL HUSAINE WA LA’NA-TUL LAAHE A’LAA A’DAAA-E-HIM WA QATA-LATE-HIM AJMA-E’EN.", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللهِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلهِ وَلَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَاللهُ اَكْبَرُ، اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمّدٍ، سَلَامُ اللهِ عَلَی الْحُسَیْنِ وَعَلٰی اَوْلَادِ الْحُسَیْنِ وَعَلٰی اَصْحَابِ الْحُسَیْنِ وَلَعْنَۃُ اللهِ عَلٰی اَعْدَآئِهِمْ وَقَتَلَتِهِمْ اَجْمَعِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "Arabi